query: Show revenue performance by technical business unit
sql:
SELECT
    SUM(cisco_stage_app.metrics.revenue) AS total_revenue, cisco_stage_app.metrics.technical_business_unit
FROM cisco_stage_app.metrics
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.metric_id = cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics.metric_id
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.metric_id = cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside.metric_id
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.metric_id = cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics.metric_id
GROUP BY cisco_stage_app.metrics.technical_business_unit
